               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Prisoner.</hi> A man in a fustian coat said, "Do you want to earn 3<hi rend="italic">d</hi>." I said, "Yes;" he said, "Go and get that coat, I have paid for it." I wanted to show them the man, and they <hi rend="italic">shoved</hi> me back. <hi rend="italic">Witness.</hi> He said there was a man—we came out, and looked round, but saw no one of the de<lb></lb>scription he gave.</p>
